        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\ntitle\n&lt;size:16&gt;&lt;b&gt;UC-01: Register Account - Activity Diagram&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/size&gt;\nend title\n\n|User (Buyer/Seller)|\nstart\n\n:Navigate to SmartTech homepage and click &#39;Register&#39;;\n\n:System displays registration form;\n\n:Complete all required fields and select account type;\n\n:Click &#39;Create Account&#39;;\n\n|System|\n:Validate input (format, email uniqueness, password strength);\n\nif (Email already registered?) then (yes)\n  :Display error: \&quot;Email already in use\&quot;;\n  stop\nelse (no)\nendif\n\nif (Password meets strength requirements?) then (no)\n  :Display inline validation error;\n  stop\nelse (yes)\nendif\n\n:Create user account with status &#39;Unverified&#39;;\n\n:Send verification email (unique token, valid 24h);\n\n:Display confirmation page instructing user to check email;\n\n|User|\n:Click verification link in email;\n\n|System|\nif (Token valid and not expired?) then (no)\n  :Display expiry notice with &#39;Resend Verification Email&#39; button;\n  stop\nelse (yes)\nendif\n\n:Validate token and set account status to &#39;Active&#39;;\n\n:Redirect user to their dashboard;\n\nstop\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="U2y3R0-jDhVh8ACwDD4h-1">
